{"type": "article", "id": 26859, "title": "黑胶唱片收纳盒", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-16T06:45:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607130032IfMNQ1Cb2Vxrekyg.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>如果你是个黑胶唱片的收藏者，不妨来看看这个专门为保存和展示黑胶唱片而设计的收纳盒 flipbin。盒子的一边被设计成少许倾斜，让你能够像是在唱片店那样浏览自己的藏品。flipbin 目前仍在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/flipbin/flipbintm-a-new-home-for-the-vinyl-youre-now-playi\">Kickstarter</a> 上进行众筹，型号 33 与 45（数字意味着它们最大可以容纳的唱片数）的最低价分别为 59 和 39 美元。美中不足的是它不支持寄往美国以外的地区。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130030Kc9Igjdq4E0WwPpD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713003087PqZjR5z9dav103.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52685185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130031eUl7Qzq29sbT0mEN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130031TA2Di3Mv5htbpn8Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n\n"}